# License notice

This repository contains the frontend UI of the MES/ERP system built for
Kingsley Beverage FZCO (Dubai), shown as a disconnected demo: it runs entirely
in the browser against a fetch interceptor, and all data is fabricated - no
production data, credentials, customers, suppliers or documents are included.

Published with Kingsley Beverage FZCO's permission for portfolio demonstration
only. This code is NOT licensed for reuse, copying or redistribution. All
rights remain with Kingsley Beverage FZCO.